creator: Alicia Stuart Aspinwall
description:
LibriVox recording of Short Stories for Short People by Alicia Stuart Aspinwall.
Read in English by NarratorJenny; Raymond Cockle; Domenica Campbell; pennykoons; Jesus Marquez; Kristin Gjerløw; Reeses118; April Walters; James K. White; Phil Chenevert; Sharon C.; Lynne Thompson; Marc Rasi
This is a collection of short stories by Alicia Aspinwall. - Summary by Carolin
For further information, including links to online text, reader information, RSS feeds, CD cover or other formats (if available), please go to the LibriVox catalog page for this recording.

For more free audio books or to become a volunteer reader, visit LibriVox.org.
